s-fans-have-just-discovered-what-debut-album-cover-star-chris-mcclure-is-doing-now-3832047">对唱片的封面明星所能感到困惑现在</a>。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lola-young-cover-arctic-monkeys-i-wanna-be-yours-on-siriusxm-3836220">观看Lola Young Cover Arctic Monkeys的“我想成为您的Siriusxm”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
