92x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/megan_thee_stallion-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·泰恩（Megan Thee）</a>在与YouTuber和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tory-Lanez">Tory Lanez的</a>支持者Milagro Gramz的第一轮比赛中取得了成功。</p><p> 10月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-sues-youtuber-over-alleged-tory-lanez-lies-and-deepfake-porn-causing-intentional-infliction-of-emotional-distress-3808487">说唱歌手对格拉姆兹（Milagro Elizabeth Cooper）提起诉讼</a>，指控她与莱恩斯（Lanez）分享了梅根（Megan）的深层色情片和蔓延性。该诉讼还指责格拉姆兹“网络群，有意造成情绪困扰以及侵犯隐私”。</p><p>现在，佛罗里达州的一名法官裁定，梅根在提出了一个“令人信服的案件”后，可以继续对格拉姆兹提起诉讼，即博客作者在关于说唱歌手的帖子中以“鲁ck对真相的无视事实”行事。</p><p>首席法官塞西莉亚·奥尔顿加（Cecilia Altonaga）在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/megan-thee-stallion-tory-lanez-blogger-lawsuit-moves-forward-1235259083/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>滚石公司</i></a>获得的法院文件中还说，格拉姆斯的职位“描绘了一项运动，而不是新闻业”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3822018" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822018" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822018" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage.jpg" alt="梅根你种马。图片来源：Jamie McCarthy/Wireimage" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.c