基于法雷尔·威廉姆斯（Pharrell Williams）的童年的电影音乐剧在后期制作https://www.nme.com/news/film/movie-musical------------------派上 - 威廉姆斯 - 卫生局部生产Poppy BurtonSat, 08 Feb 2025 10:27:31 +0000 Film NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3836207 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Pharell Williams" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “当我们所有人进入编辑室时，我们共同认为没有前进的道路来讲述我们最初设想的这个故事的版本”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/movie-musical-based-on-pharrell-williams-childhood-scrapped-in-post-production-3836207">基于法雷尔·威廉姆斯（Pharrell Williams）的童年时期，后期制作中取消的电影音乐剧</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Pharell Williams" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-pharell-williams-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>基于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">法雷尔·威廉姆斯（Pharrell Williams）</a>的童年时代的电影音乐剧<em>《戈尔登》（Golden</em> ）被废弃了后期制作。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-listid="757" data-list-defn-props="{"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-interview-trailer-lego-piece-by-piece-3762433"><b>Pharrell Williams向我们介绍了他在Lego中的传记片《著作》：“这对我来说是一次了不起的历史体验”</b></a></li></ul><p>该项目最初名为<em>Atlantis，</em>由Michel Gondry（<em>一尘不染的永恒阳光</em>）执导，据报道，Universal Pictures的戏剧发行，据报道于5月5日挂钩。其长明星包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/kelvin-harrison-jr-chevalier-martin-luther-king-interview-3452700">Kelvin Harrison Jr. Kelvin Harrison Jr.</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halle-bailey">Halle Bailey</a> ，Halle Bailey，DA DA，DA， Vine Joy Randolph，Brian Tyree Henry，JanelleMonáe，Missy Elliott，Quinta Brunson， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anderson-paak">Anderson .Paak</a>和Jaboukie Young-White。</p><p>早在11月，威廉姆斯（Williams）在接受<a href="https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/pharrell-and-michel-gondrys-golden-is-a-celebration-of-black-joy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>帝国的</em></a>一次采访中提供了这部电影的第一个也是唯一的一瞥，在那里他将电影与<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-interview-trailer-lego-piece-by-piece-3762433">作品《著作》（The Time）区</a>分开来，</em>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡（Oscar）</a>执导的纪录片人摩根·尼维尔（Morgan Neville）的一生乐高传记片，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daft-punk-to-feature-in-pharrell-williams-lego-biopic-piece-by-piece-3790136">在Daft Punk</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwen-stefani">Gwen Stefani</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timbaland">Timbaland</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">Justin Timberlake</a>等。</p><p>威廉姆斯说：“&#39;wire priece&#39;是关于我的生活，而&#39;Golden&#39;是我长大的社区。这是1977年夏天在弗吉尼亚海滩举行的音乐探险。” </p><figure id="attachment_3794992" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794992" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3794992" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pharrell-jemal-countess-1.jpg" alt="Pharrell" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pharrell-jemal-countess-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pharrell-jemal-countess-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pharrell-jemal-countess-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pharrell-jemal-countess-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pharrell-jemal-countess-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pharrell-jemal-countess-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3794992" class="wp-caption-text">安大略省多伦多 -  9月10日：帕雷尔·威廉姆斯（Pharrell Williams）于2024年9月10日在威尔士公主剧院（Wales of Princess of Princess of Princes）在安大略省多伦多的威尔士剧院首映。 （Jemal Countess/Getty Images的照片）</figcaption></figure><p> “这是一个关于自我发现和追求梦想的成年故事，但比这更神奇。这是对黑人生活，黑人文化的庆祝活动，最重要的是黑人喜悦。”</p><p>据报道，环球影业为与威廉姆斯长期合作的一部分提供了创造力，后者在<em>卑鄙的</em><em>ME</em>专营权中撰写和表演，现在将吞下已经在生产上花费的大约2000万美元的成本（每种<a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/news/pharrell-movie-shut-down-michel-gondry-golden-1236300426/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>品种</em></a>）。</p><p>各种消息人士告诉出版物，这部电影在制片人和冈德里达成一致的协议之后就被关闭了，这部电影不符合期望，而工作室不会发布该项目或将其购买给其他买家。 </p><figure id="attachment_3793819" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793819" style="width: 1392px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793819" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-2023-Getty.jpg" alt="水节法雷尔（Pharrell）" width="1392" height="884" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-2023-Getty.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-2023-Getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-2023-Getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-2023-Getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Pharrell-2023-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793819" class="wp-caption-text">法雷尔（Pharrell）在2023年的《水节》中演出。学分：肯德尔·华纳（Kendall Warner）/弗吉尼亚人/论坛报新闻服务通过盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>“当我们所有人进入编辑室时，我们共同决定没有前进的道路来讲述我们最初设想的这个故事的版本，”威廉姆斯和冈德里在昨天（2月7日）的联合声明中告诉<em>《综艺》</em> 。</p><p> “我们感谢才华横溢的演员和工作人员的所有辛勤工作。虽然我们感到失望，但我们无法交付这部电影，但我们在Universal上有令人难以置信的合作伙伴，并将很快以不同的身份进行合作。”</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-williams-morgan-neville-interview-trailer-lego-piece-by-piece-3762433">去年接受<em>NME的</em>采访</a>中，这位“快乐”歌手解释说，<em>按作品</em>开展工作是“历史的惊人经历”。</p><p>他还称赞摩根·内维尔（Morgan Neville）执行自己的愿景，他说：“我不能告诉你让这个精湛的讲故事的人真正理解我的生活有多谦虚。它一直到处都是，对我来说很有意义，但对大多数人来说不是。他能够用彩色做到这一点 - 砖块的砖块。”</p><p>这部电影的许多节日放映<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/peta-speak-out-protesting-pharrell-williams-lego-movie-stop-being-complicit-in-cruelty-3806785">被动物权利活动家打断</a>，抗议活动与歌手作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pharrell-named-mens-creative-director-of-louis-vuitton-3399133">时装屋Louis Vuitton的男子创意总监的角色有关。</a>来自PETA的代表呼吁威廉姆斯停止“残酷同谋”，指的是路易·威登（Louis Vuitton）使用动物皮和毛皮。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/movie-musical-based-on-pharrell-williams-childhood-scrapped-in-post-production-3836207">基于法雷尔·威廉姆斯（Pharrell Williams）的童年时期，后期制作中取消的电影音乐剧</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo https://www.nme.com/news/film/cynthia-erivo-denies-wicked-wicked-wicked-performance-rumours-rumours-this-feels-feels-feels-feels-like-wishful-wishful-to-me-3836197？ Cynthia-erivo-denies-to-oscars-performance-rumours-tim-tim-feels tike tike this-feish-felly-thinking-to-me to-mePoppy Burton Sat, 08 Feb 2025 09:27:40 +0000 Film NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3836197 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我不知道为什么我们会这样做，因为我们的歌没有提名”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cynthia-erivo-denies-wicked-oscars-performance-rumours-this-feels-like-wishful-thinking-to-me-3836197">辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo）否认“邪恶”的奥斯卡表演谣言：“这对我来说就像是一厢情愿的想法”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo）否认声称她打算在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">2025年的奥斯卡颁奖典礼</a>上表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>邪恶的</em></a>歌曲，并说这个想法就像“一厢情愿”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2025-nominations-full-list-3831350">奥斯卡2025提名 - 请参阅完整列表</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年的仪式<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的现场表演</a>，在该类别中提名的艺术家将在整个晚上演出，以获得颁奖典礼。取而代之的是，该节目引起了歌曲作者的“个人思考”的关注。</p><p>尽管大多数奥斯卡提名都在今年早些时候透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/elton-john-pharrell-williams-trent-reznor-among-oscars-2025-shortlist-for-best-original-song-3823258">但最佳原创歌曲和最佳原创乐谱的入围名单在12月揭幕</a>。在最佳原创歌曲入围名单的艺术家中，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">Elton John</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">Pharrell Williams</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trent-reznor">Trent Reznor</a>和Atticus Ross， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>等。</p><p>几个主要的大片在入围名单中列出了最佳原始得分，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2"><em>角斗士2</em></a> ，<em>挑战者</em>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/beetlejuice-beetlejuice"><em>贝特利朱吉斯·贝特利朱吉斯</em></a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/alien-romulus"><em>《外星人：romulus：Romulus》</em></a>和《 Erivo Starring <em>Wicked》</em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756649" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756649" style="width: 1317px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756649" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande.jpg" alt="邪恶" width="1317" height="836" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande.jpg 1317w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1317px) 100vw, 1317px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756649" class="wp-caption-text"> Ariana Grande和Cynthia Erivo在“邪恶”中。图片来源：环球影城。</figcaption></figure><p>昨晚（2月7日），她在批评家选择奖的红地毯上与<a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/news/cynthia-erivo-denies-wicked-performance-oscars-1236301048/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>综艺节目</em></a>进行了交谈，鉴于该学院希望通过自己和联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a>表演的<em>邪恶</em>数字的混音打开电视转播。</p><p> “为什么每个人都说这句话？当被问及报告时，她说。 “这对我个人来说就像一厢情愿。我们为什么要唱歌？”</p><p>当被问及她是否与学院谈论表演时，她很快就否认了这一点。 “不！” Erivo回答说：“人们问我是否要在奥斯卡颁奖典礼上唱歌。我不知道为什么我们会这样做，因为我们的歌没有提名。那不会发生。我不知道该告诉你什么。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFy4ES5JFlo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0